{"tid":1665572,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"魔警而家既策略, 捉勇武為主線, 拉唔拉夠人數都唔緊要","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T00:32:23.000Z","uid":76310,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e83dc7459d2e3bcdfb1083293a6e49d74447d54d","tid":1665572,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"魔警而家既策略, 似捉勇武為主線<br />\n(利申: 今日咁岩去尖沙咀欣賞海景, 又去旺角行街)<br />\n<br />\n魔警今日既行動, 比以前收斂<br />\n無前幾次咁狼咁狠, 見人就拉<br />\n個人覺得, 佢地認為咁多人, 個個拉晒咩<br />\n今日魔警甚至退後都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n佢地放大量既鬼混入, 重點跟著入面既勇武和搵機會捉你地<br />\n所以各位勇武要小心, 行事時, 要開遮陣, 快速完事(最好無人知無人影到)<br />\n完事後就閃, 唔好戀戰. <br />\n只係你自己唔覺, 但事實好多鬼混入左, 專跟勇武同搵機會捉你地<br />\n<br />\n各位勇武手足要小心"},{"pid":"16229bcea54a1c28f721b86f89a913bfd6bfcab1","tid":1665572,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36fa0d9490770ab8516047d6158a0289022d154","tid":1665572,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:26:18.000Z","msg":"係 避無可避 真係要小心 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea692d3dac29e17d9585494a0a562795ad319a6","tid":1665572,"uid":100205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"d5cccffe343b958207f38b8fd2d3cfebcda0f7d0","tid":1665572,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9831aaa03dbe4df80e09f9a50c62bbddd9bd0f17","tid":1665572,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f81941740ab74c85c82acc64c78e5679d0876831","tid":1665572,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b