":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n快手做完野混入人群，記住要反跟蹤"},{"pid":"d9e26e077c1c349e289e59f5663195c1ca60f542","tid":1665572,"uid":319380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"和理非散，勇武都應該散。<br />\n最好天黑前返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好為左裝修多2間鋪而坐10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491da1b98b575d3487d2721d6b10f69607b7fece","tid":1665572,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb09637c188cda49d5065be981f8ed4822655eb7","tid":1665572,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"唔覺侷地有收歛<br />\n只係今日多人果時唔敢伸個尻頭出黎<br />\n人少少又發作"},{"pid":"9eea29c250c7163ae2b415fc8c5c63089fabe099","tid":1665572,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"收不收歛不是重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點, 勇武手足完事後即閃, 即散, 行事要快, 最好乜都影唔到就走左<br />\n唔好戀戰</span><br />\n其他街坊, 手足, 自然會有人戀戰"},{"pid":"3b500cf817c943c8ce59df3fdd7182651161dd7f","tid":1665572,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb59ac4cbd2f76d3a5da73559506f87892d1ab01","tid":1665572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a43f5c606a1730a2bde2a61f113b193d0048363","tid":1665572,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5d65af60c156006c26635fac2bb45c103b8382","tid":1665572,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"Push"